{"tid":1464323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發起全球  boycott made in china  運動","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T02:52:28.000Z","uid":149496,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf4b250928c7da12e2cab438f3e5dfdddac8d5d","tid":1464323,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"不以香港反送中為主角  而且要直指中國共產黨嘅罪行<br />\n<br />\n文宣例子:<br />\n中國係國際貿易賺到大部分嘅錢都進入左中共政府或者權貴嘅荷包  人民實際分到嘅只係豆零<br />\n<br />\n中共賺到錢後就有能力驅動佢嘅維隱同鎮壓人民嘅機械<br />\n直接嘅: 香港人  新疆維吾爾人  西藏人<br />\n間接嘅: 中共支援緊北韓政權  間接就幫緊北韓政府奴役北韓人民<br />\n<br />\n任何人如果購買made in china 貨物就等於俾緊錢中共政權  等佢有能力打壓人民  咁就係中共嘅幫兇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求意見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可行嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求文宣</span></span>"},{"pid":"83eeea617a433e8d4d35798d9ab55f5f1a23b93b","tid":1464323,"uid":149496,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"有鬼佬問what do you want  /  what can i do about it<br />\n<br />\n就係boycott made in china"},{"pid":"c35fbc405bd114744bf448d117cae4b9a38dee76","tid":1464323,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a2ab8109dcefa26d92255b5d3b01e561ee659c","tid":1464323,"uid":111009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"好困難我覺得<br />\n外國人比起我地一定無咁憎中共<br />\n第一自己人都做唔到 外國人點會做?<br />\n例子就係我成日都見到手足仲食緊m記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二就係中共產品真係好廣 用緊d iphone都有零件係made in China <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402f